			  			<h3>Page Navigation</h3>
			  			<p>At the bottom of the scenario you will find a pagination bar displaying a page for each question. You must complete the current question before before the next becomes available (question number turns blue).</p>
			  			<p>Once you have completed all questions you can select 'Show Score' to see your results.</p>
			  			<p>You can go to another scenario before completing the one in use, then return later to finish. Your progress is remembered.</p>
			  		</div>
