			  			<p>You <b>score</b> is displayed and compared to the average score of all users to date. There is no passing score used for the online scenario simulator.</p>
			  			<p>Your 'Information Gathering' and 'Decision Making' points are compared to total possible points.</p>
			  			<p>All questions are now displayed with all answers that include point values for each.</b>
